 =&gt; No checking in the departure. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSolomon都有講話禁止中國航班飛美國，不過要請佢留意埋香港：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=7970c76b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue%2Fstatus%2F1221454591335653377&h=ce7d6a4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue/status/1221454591335653377</a><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"0cdbd237969061622490d936740b6eb2e1641f34","tid":1845070,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【梁卓偉食屎】蒙古國宣布關閉邊境   澳門下令驅逐湖北旅客</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1505061_1_L_20200127130114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1505061_1_L_20200127130114.jpg&h=5998ed3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙古國宣布，從今天起關閉與中國接壤的邊境通道，包括汽車和行人通道，並呼籲取消所有公眾集會。另外，蒙古今天起，關閉所有大學和教育機構，直至3月2日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505061-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505061-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420RmVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=7fc3f394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505061-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed675296\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505061-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳門下令湖北旅客離開澳門 否則強制進入隔離營</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://apple01.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/774-1-696x392.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple01.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F774-1-696x392.png&h=b9716801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是一份昨天流出的澳門旅遊局通告，由澳門旅遊局局長文綺華致全澳各酒店，下令來自武漢市及湖北省的旅客於今早9:00前離開澳門，否則要入住隔離營！先莫論行動效果如何，但至少澳門有實際行動希望減低民怨，但香港呢？就係一招暉明邨？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://apple01.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/83238336_2508125362767377_512583322912686080_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple01.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F83238336_2508125362767377_512583322912686080_n.jpg&h=380760e7&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}